summary: This document is a warrant certificate that allows the holder to purchase up to 33,404 shares of common stock in Off the Hook YS Inc. at an exercise price of $5.00 per share, starting from May 11, 2026, until November 12, 2030. The warrant includes restrictions on transferring the warrant for 180 days after the initial exercise date and provides definitions for various terms used throughout the document. It also outlines the procedures for exercising the warrant, including a cashless exercise option.
